  "detailed_description": "<h1>Play New Game Demo!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/e9fe09ea36d77aec972e0223cf404937.avif?t=1771536404\" width=600 height=280 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Thunder Ronin Is A Samurai Souls-like Boss Rush.<br>On Your Way to Take Revenge On Your Familty.<br>Slash, Deflect, and Dash Through Powerful Foes.<br>fighting in ancient japan between sakura trees and the glow of the moon.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT</h2>Deflect strikes with you katana. the greatest counter to any danger that comes before you is to use the skill you honed after years of practice that allows you to perfectly block the damage from an attack an become more focused afterwards<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/344a23692e553f27bfe1619fd343329e.poster.avif?t=1771536404\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/344a23692e553f27bfe1619fd343329e.webm?t=1771536404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/344a23692e553f27bfe1619fd343329e.mp4?t=1771536404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRANSFORMATIONS</h2>Fight the fury of the elements. you family are masters of the elements and can transform into dangerous foes. you must defeat them to get to your father<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/03e0b35c91442be23bd6f7a8ea1ad36c.poster.avif?t=1771536404\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/03e0b35c91442be23bd6f7a8ea1ad36c.webm?t=1771536404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/03e0b35c91442be23bd6f7a8ea1ad36c.mp4?t=1771536404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THUNDER</h2>Unleash the element of thunder, as the Thunder Ronin you have the innate ability of lightning in you blood. focus your mind and you may be able to unleash it<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/01a6775d0cf750d0ac9ca3c8682acca2.poster.avif?t=1771536404\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/01a6775d0cf750d0ac9ca3c8682acca2.webm?t=1771536404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744340/extras/01a6775d0cf750d0ac9ca3c8682acca2.mp4?t=1771536404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
